# NestJS Conventions

## Path Aliases
- `@app/*` → src/app/*
- `@common/*` → src/common/*
- `@config` → src/configs/index.ts
- `@configs/*` → src/configs/*
- `@modules/*` → src/modules/*
- `@router` → src/router/router.module.ts

## Naming
- Class: PascalCase
- File: kebab-case
- DTO suffix: RequestDto / ResponseDto

## Architecture
- Repository → data access, injects TypeORM Repository
- Service → business logic, injects Repository
- Controller → HTTP layer, injects Service

## Pagination
- Use `@PaginationOffsetQuery` or `@PaginationCursorQuery` for list endpoints
- Use `createTypeOrmPaginationAdapter(repository)` with `PaginationService.offset/cursor`
